summary: Was only a matter of time before i got around to these two, based on the cooperative hunting that have been documented between...
caption: Was only a matter of time before i got around to these two, based on the cooperative hunting that have been documented between American badgers and coyotes in the west, in which coyotes will track down and chase prairie dogs into their burrows, where the badger will than pursue the animals. Either the badger will catch them underground or chase them back out into the coyotes jowls.

summary: Ya know what’s weird? When I originally heard of Aggretsuko, the characters, and the ships and stuff never registered with me....
body:
Ya know what’s weird? When I originally heard of Aggretsuko, the characters, and the ships and stuff never registered with me. The only thing that got me at first was the mention of metal. The character singing death metal (well, an interpretation of death metal, it’s really more thrash than anything) was pretty interesting, but I totally forgot about it. Then the thing that got me into the show was, of all things, Retsuaida. I came for the death metal, I stayed for the ship.

I’m not even into death metal necessarily! I’m a power metal fan, usually. :P
